Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有一辆车 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}There was a car
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,上头有三个人，和所有的车一样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and it had three men in it and it did what most cars do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它从一个方向开来然后开走 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}It came in one direction and left in the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我能告诉你的就是这些 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That's all I can tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:24:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我能告诉你的细节，都是关于这个地方的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}The only detail I can tell you is the detail that pertains to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我能告诉你他们喝了什么 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I can tell you what they drank.
