Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.40,0:24:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我能告诉你他们说了什么，如果他们说了的话 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I can tell you what they said, if they said anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我听到他们说了什么的话 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and if I heard what it was that they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.48,0:24:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说什么了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.84,0:24:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么也没说，他们没在这停 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}They didn't say anything. They didn't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定很喜欢那辆车，亲爱的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You must really love that car, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.12,0:24:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时代还有什么值得兴奋的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What a thing to get worked up about in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.04,0:24:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么喜爱那辆车 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What is it about the car \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}that you love so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.80,0:24:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我吗 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.08,0:24:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字，亲爱的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What's your name, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.04,0:25:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别傻了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Oh, don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.32,0:25:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是气坏了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Now you're just being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.08,0:25:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你对这车干嘛了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What are you doing with this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.56,0:25:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我哥的车 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}It's my brother's car.
