Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.08,0:26:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.16,0:26:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Henry在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Where's Henry at?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.92,0:26:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是你哥，他在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Who's your brother? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.80,0:26:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我他在哪，否则杀了你 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You tell me where he is, or I'm gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.20,0:26:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.64,0:26:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这没有医生 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}There's no doctor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.44,0:26:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该是这个小镇最有用的人 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm about the most useful person in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.08,0:26:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当你知道离这个小镇最近的医生有多远 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}If that gives you any idea how far from having a doctor this town is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.00,0:26:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别的地哪有医生 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Is there a doctor somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.32,0:26:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你买点东西 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.32,0:26:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉过你我这卖什么，有啤酒有喝的有别的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I told you what I've got. I've got tins of things and drinks and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.16,0:26:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,整天处理搞你这破事 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I have to deal with this shit all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.40,0:26:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.64,0:26:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没跟你开玩笑 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.36,0:26:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么说“拜托”都行，但我没在开玩笑 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You can say "please" all you like, but I'm not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.44,0:26:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，从货柜上给自己挑点东西 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Now, pick yourself something off the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.40,0:27:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,给Benny结账 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Pay Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.24,0:27:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,医生在山上，出门向东 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}There's a doctor in them hills there. Head east,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.64,0:27:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沿着朝山的路走，就到了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and follow the road that looks like it leads to those hills, you'll get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.48,0:27:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,到那有个大黄标志，上面写着“人苠医院” \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}It's got a big yellow fridge out the front, says "Peeples" written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.12,0:28:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,兜里枪放下来 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Pull the gun out of your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.72,0:28:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我车里有个小孩需要救治 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I've got a kid in the car who needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.68,0:29:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,兜里的枪掏出来，放在地上 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Pull the gun out of your pants and put it on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.48,0:29:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要救治 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}He needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.40,0:29:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你朋友吗 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Is this man your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.00,0:30:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,医疗费多少 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}How much do you want for doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.00,0:30:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你的钱 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I don't want your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.08,0:30:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我过没有货币的生活过得很好 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I've gotten pretty good living without money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.32,0:32:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须把这些孩子养在这起来 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I have to keep these guys locked up in here now for the most part,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.68,0:32:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不然人们会把它们当肉吃了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}'cause people take them for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.52,0:32:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,它们来我这 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}These guys came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.96,0:32:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的主人们扔下它们 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}People just drop them off
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.36,0:32:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,说要离开一阵，让我帮忙照料 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and ask me to look after them while they went away somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.12,0:33:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说要去做别的什么事 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}or because they had to go somewhere or do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.40,0:33:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一去不复返 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and none of them ever came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.00,0:33:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们应该都是去挣钱了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I guess they've gone looking for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.12,0:33:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我帮你看下你的伤口？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Do you want me to take a look at your cuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.08,0:33:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.40,0:34:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.96,0:34:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}How ya going?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.76,0:34:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我还行 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.20,0:34:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，愿不愿意坐下来我帮你检查看看 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Um, do you wanna take a chair while I have a look at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.40,0:35:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,疼吧 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.48,0:35:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿开吧 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Do you want to take your hand away?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.48,0:35:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不是太糟糕 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That doesn't look too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.32,0:35:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很好，你只需要让伤口保持干净就行了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That looks good. You just need to keep this clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.88,0:35:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你哥在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Tell me where your brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.72,0:35:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我会带你去的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'll take you to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.24,0:35:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你哥在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Tell me where your brother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.44,0:35:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.52,0:35:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他去了南边，离这很远，我会带你去的，我保证 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}He's gone south a long way from here.I'll take you to him, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.72,0:35:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你找件衣服 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm just gonna get you a T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.04,0:36:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,起来，上路 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Get up. We're leaving.
