Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.76,0:36:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.92,0:36:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,又一辆 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That's two cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.24,0:36:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们多快到这- 一分钟，也许 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}- How long till they're here? - A minute, maybe.
