Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.12,0:36:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把你来福枪拿出来 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Get your rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.52,0:36:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你认识他们吗 - 把你来福枪拿出来 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}- DOROTHY: Do you know them? - Go and get your rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.84,0:37:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我发生什么事了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.32,0:37:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是什么人 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.52,0:37:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,起来，上路 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Get up. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.00,0:38:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,起来 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.72,0:39:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.04,0:39:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.00,0:40:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,搞点吃的？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}REY: Go and get some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.16,0:40:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在告诉我 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You're gonna start talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.28,0:40:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.40,0:41:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别他妈什么什么，我们这是去哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Don't fucking "what" me. Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.64,0:41:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,除了已经告诉你的，别的都不能说 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I can't tell you nothing more than I already told you.
