Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.00,0:41:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就告诉我 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Start fucking talking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.72,0:41:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老公别这样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.80,0:41:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你其实也不知道我们在哪是吧 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Do you even know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.92,0:41:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么？ - 我们在哪？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}- What? - Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.68,0:41:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.96,0:41:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.36,0:41:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈不知道？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You don't fucking know?
