Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.48,0:43:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才问那个姐姐怎么去Carloon \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I just asked that lady how to get to Carloon from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.52,0:43:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你听得见我和她说话 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I was gonna do that anyway and you would've heard me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.64,0:43:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你也可以自己去问，看看我是不是在说谎 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and you would've asked her what I said, figured out what I said anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.04,0:43:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我还是先告诉你 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I was gonna tell you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.00,0:43:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,情况不是很乐观 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You wanna know so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.32,0:43:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道去了Carloon之后具体位置在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}But you don't know exactly where in Carloon we're going exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.36,0:43:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以局面还是我在控制 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}so, I'm still in control here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.48,0:43:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道去了Carloon之后具体位置在哪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You don't know exactly where in Carloon we're going,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.28,0:44:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你得带我和你一起去 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}so you got to take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.68,0:44:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我会带你一起去，因为如果到了Carloon \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm taking you with me because if I get to Carloon
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.80,0:44:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥不在那，我会割了你的喉咙 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and your brother's not there, \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm gonna slit your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.84,0:44:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你那么想对我哥干坏事 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What you want with my \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}brother so bad, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.36,0:44:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.00,0:44:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Rey，你是想问这个？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm Rey. Is that what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.20,0:44:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么会在这？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.04,0:44:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我和我哥从矿上出来，和其他所有人一样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Me and my brother came out for \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}the mines. Like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.44,0:44:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥为什么在Carloon \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why's your brother in Carloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.04,0:44:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他本来要去的地方 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That's where he was gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.56,0:44:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你在这，而你哥在Carloon \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why are you here and your \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}brother's in Carloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.24,0:45:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们非常着急走 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}They had to get going \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}in a big hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.52,0:45:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.24,0:45:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么这么着急走 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why did he have to get going in a big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.60,0:45:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，我不能说 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I don't know. I can't talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.92,0:45:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你个这么着急去Carloon \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why did your brother have to get to Carloon in a big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.44,0:45:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我不能说 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I can't talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.20,0:45:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好，不管他想做什么 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Well, whatever it was he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.60,0:45:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他就去做了，同时把你扔在这等死 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}you got left here to die \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}while he was doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.68,0:45:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是这样的 - 是吗 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}- It didn't happen like that.- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.56,0:45:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}How did it happen, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.08,0:45:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能说，快别问了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I can't talk about it no more,just stop asking about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.64,0:46:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我相信老天爷，我哥Henry也信 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}'Cause I believe in God and I know Henry believes in God,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.80,0:46:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Henry不会看着我受伤不管的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and there's no harm Henry would want to see me come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.52,0:46:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信这一点 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I believe in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.60,0:46:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那看看你肚子上那窟窿，Henry在哪呢 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Yet look at the harm you've come to and where's Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.24,0:46:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他在等我 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}He's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.40,0:46:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他没在等你 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}He's not waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.28,0:46:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他在 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.84,0:46:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，他没在等 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.48,0:46:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你老天爷给了你什么 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'll tell you what God's given you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.00,0:46:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他塞了个子弹进你肚子 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}He's put a bullet in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.20,0:46:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把你抛弃给了我，而我根本不认识你 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And he's abandoned you out here \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}to me, who feels nothing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.00,0:46:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你明天死了什么事也不会发生 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I couldn't give a fuck \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}if you die tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.68,0:46:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷给你一个没在等你的老哥 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}God gave you a brother \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}who's not waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.64,0:46:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,给你一个现在恐怕都想不起你来的老哥 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}He gave you a brother who's not \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}even thinking about you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.00,0:47:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只因为你和他是从同一个肚子里出来的所以你们是兄弟 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Just because you and him came \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}out of the same woman's hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.92,0:47:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在所有有意义的事是 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}The only thing that means \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}anything right now
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.68,0:47:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这而他不在 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}is that I'm here and he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.36,0:47:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥扔下你不管，让你去死 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Your brother left you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.64,0:47:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,人们都在干这事 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That's what people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.12,0:47:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你不学着去抗争，你就真的快死了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You don't learn to fight, your \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}death's gonna come real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.04,0:52:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别开枪了！ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Stop shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.32,0:52:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想去抗争 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I just wanted to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.60,0:52:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想去抗争 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I just wanted to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.88,0:52:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.36,0:52:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,走着 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.08,0:55:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那个姐姐说，过去去那要花大概8小时 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That lady said it would take about eight hours to get there, in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.88,0:55:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在可能会更久，因为那些老路都荒废了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}{\i1}But it might take longer now 'cause a lot of them old roads ain't there no more.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.00,0:56:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在路都很烂，你开不快 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And all the roads are bad now anyways \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}so you can't drive fast on 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.80,0:56:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她说可能要8或者9个小时 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}She said about eight or nine hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.60,0:56:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她不确定是8小时还是9小时 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}She wasn't sure if it was eight or nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.08,0:56:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她很不确定 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}She seemed a bit confused about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.64,0:56:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那你哥为什么还在那 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And why would he still be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.96,0:56:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那呆两个星期等人 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}He had to wait two weeks for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.32,0:56:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那有个人要见，要等两个星期 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}There's a man there he's got to meet, it's gonna take two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.52,0:56:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定是这样，还是他告诉你的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You know this? Or this is what he told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.12,0:56:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.64,0:56:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥那人不能信 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Your brother can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.04,0:56:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这事是“你知道”还是“他告诉你的” \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Is this something that you know or is this something that he told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.12,0:56:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都是 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Both those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.60,0:57:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你在矿上工作？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You work in the mines?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.12,0:57:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.88,0:57:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是做什么工作？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What do you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.64,0:57:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我过去种田，现在我在这 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I was a farmer. And now I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.80,0:57:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那你从哪学得枪，枪法这么好 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Then how come you learned how to shoot so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.44,0:57:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前当兵的吧？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You was in the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.20,0:57:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候在一个农场长大 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}When I was a little kid I grew up on a farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.52,0:57:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的邻居，Verna和Clarry，老到不行 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}We had these neighbors, real old \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}man and lady, Verna and Clarry,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.96,0:57:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是兄妹 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}they's brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.64,0:57:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的田里全是荒草 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And they lived on this \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}land that's all overgrown,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.28,0:58:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你都说不出来他们在种什么，全被荒草淹没了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}like you couldn't even tell what \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}they farmed, so overgrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.68,0:58:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarry有8台拖拉机，没有一台是正常工作的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And Clarry had these eight tractors, \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and none of them worked properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.04,0:58:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,每天早上他都把所有的拖拉机放下山，直到其中有一台开始启动 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}so every morning he'd roll each one down \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}the hill till he got one of them started
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.56,0:58:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后用能启动这台把别的拖拉机拖回来 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and then use that one to tow all \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}the others back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.44,0:58:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他每天都这样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}He did that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.20,0:58:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从来没有见过他们家人，他们死后 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And when they died, their family, \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}who we'd never met before,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.72,0:58:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的家人四处赶来，声称继承他们的房子 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}came around, cleared \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}out their house
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.68,0:58:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,最后他们发现 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and they found all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.20,0:58:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们发现许多奇怪的玩意 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}They found all this weird stuff in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.76,0:58:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,比如 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.00,0:58:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,比如50 therm \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Like 50 therm...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.56,0:58:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,热力电台阀门 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Thermionic radio valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.72,0:58:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们用在老收音机上的老阀门 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Like them real old valves \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}they used in old radios.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.48,0:58:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还有南瓜金字塔 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And pyramid of pumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.12,0:58:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有大概5000个这样稀奇古怪的玩意 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And about 5,000 of these \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}little sticks about this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.48,0:59:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,每个都用报纸包着，用绳子挂起来 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And each wrapped up in newspaper and \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}tied up at the ends with baling twine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.56,0:59:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么跟我说这些 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.84,0:59:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是记起来了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I just remembered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.60,0:59:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得很有趣 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}It interested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.60,0:59:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什么事都必须意味着什么嘛 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Not everything has to be about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.64,0:59:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着不去想那个死去的女孩，但我控制不住 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm tryin' to stop thinking about \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}that little girl who died, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.00,1:00:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.96,1:00:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可我控制不住 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}But I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.96,1:00:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你别控制，是你该想的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You shouldn't stop thinking about her.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.80,1:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该永远记得这个被你带走的生命 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You should never stop thinking \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}about a life you've taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.92,1:00:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你该承受的代价 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}It's the price you pay for taking it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.80,1:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样，骚逼 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That's it, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.60,1:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,从睁开眼睛开始 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Let's start with the eyelids.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.08,1:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,趴过去，手放在背后 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I want you to roll over onto your \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}front, put your hands behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.56,1:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢做 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And do it slow.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.44,1:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在做！ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And do it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.72,1:04:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你啥时候才开口说话，婊子 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}{\i1}SOLDIER: When are you gonna say something, cunt?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.88,1:04:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}{\i1}It's over.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.36,1:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你完蛋了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}It's over for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.76,1:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.96,1:04:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，你知道 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That's good that you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.40,1:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道吗 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Do you know it, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.24,1:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我知道，小哥 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Oh, I know it, champ.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.00,1:04:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I told you it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.64,1:04:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你也完蛋了吗 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Do you know it's over for you, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.92,1:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我完蛋，我早就完蛋了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Whatever you think's over for \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}me was over a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.24,1:04:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那你呢 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm asking about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.80,1:04:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在威胁我妈 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Are you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.28,1:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.08,1:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,威胁意味着什么事将会发生 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}A threat means there's still something left to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.44,1:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎么处置我 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What are you gonna do with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.84,1:05:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你会被送去悉尼 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You're going to Sydney.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.72,1:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不直接枪决我 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why don't you just shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.12,1:05:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不这样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Why don't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.80,1:05:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别人都是这么做的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That's what everyone else is doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.84,1:05:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我会把你送去悉尼 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Because me sending you to Sydney
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.04,1:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们我们在认真努力的工作，给我们发薪 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}tells Sydney there's a reason to \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}keep paying us what they pay us.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.44,1:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们简单地枪决每个我们想枪决的傻逼 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}If we just shot every \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}idiot we wanted to shoot,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.80,1:05:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那很快，他们会疑惑我们在这荒山野岭做什么 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}then pretty soon they'd start to wonder \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}what the fuck we're doing out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.96,1:05:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说，我个人不在乎你怎么样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}See, personally I don't care about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.76,1:05:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎你去不去悉尼，去了又被放了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I don't care if you get to Sydney and they \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}let you off or you bribe your way out
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.68,1:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你靠贿赂出来怎么地，最近就是这样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}or whatever the fuck they \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}do down there these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.80,1:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不在乎 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I don't give a fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.68,1:06:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我这样做是为自己 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm doing this for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.60,1:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在为自己做什么 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You're doing what for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.68,1:06:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你在为自己做什么 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You're doing what for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.12,1:06:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了自己媳妇 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I murdered my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.80,1:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟踪她去了一个男人家里 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I followed her to a man's house,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.36,1:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男的把手伸进我媳妇裙子里，我杀了他俩 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I watched him put his fingers \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}inside her and I killed 'em both.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.16,1:06:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人来找过我 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No one ever came after me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.04,1:06:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,十年前的事 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.40,1:06:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没向任何人解释过我的感受 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I never had to explain myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.04,1:06:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有因为这件事撒过谎 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}也从来没有因为这件事逃亡或躲避 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I never had to lie to anyone. \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I never had to run and hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.52,1:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是把他们埋了然后回家 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I just buried 'em in a \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}hole and I went home.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.24,1:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人来找过我 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No one ever came after me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.60,1:06:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,而这比我媳妇出轨还让我难受 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}And that hurt me more than \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}getting my heart broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.84,1:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,知道这没关系 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Knowing it didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.72,1:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你可以杀掉两个人而没有人会找上你 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Knowing you can do something like \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}that and no one comes after you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.40,1:07:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了一件和我一样的事，这应该以为着什么 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You do a thing like I did, that \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}should really mean something.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.08,1:07:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但这一切都没有意义 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}But it just doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.76,1:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，小哥 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Well, champ.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.20,1:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在Abo镇做的事，对我们来说确实是有“意义”的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Thing you did in Abo town is the \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}one thing that does matter to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.44,1:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你可以“撒谎”或者“认罪”了 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Now you can do all the lying \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}and confessing you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.32,1:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你早上醒来的时候感觉怎么样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What feeling do you have when \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}you wake up in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.12,1:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,当你的脚踏上地板 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}When your feet touch the floor?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.16,1:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,或在那之前，你躺在床上，想象你的脚踏上地板 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Or before that, when you're lying there \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}thinking about your feet hitting the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.00,1:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}What does that feel like for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.96,1:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我在说什么吗 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Do you know what I'm talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.72,1:08:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道啊，小哥，我不知道 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No, mate. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.04,1:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You don't?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.12,1:08:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道，小哥。我不知道你他妈在说什么。 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No, mate. I don't know what \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}the fuck you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.36,1:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}MAN: What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.12,1:08:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,咻 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Phew!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.24,1:08:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.20,1:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这么容易？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.20,1:08:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我用不用再射他一发确认一下 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Do I shoot him again just to be sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.68,1:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.08,1:08:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.24,1:08:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太简单了，总共才三个人 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}That was easy. There were only three of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.64,1:08:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,本来还以为会困难点 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Thought it was gonna be way more harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.04,1:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你绑着呢？ \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You tied up?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.48,1:09:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我偷偷杀了这两个 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I snuck up on these two.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.52,1:09:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他俩刚在这聊着呢 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}They were just hanging there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.44,1:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我从那边门进来的 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I came through the gate there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.44,1:09:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我在围墙底下挖了个洞，可以从这滑出来 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I dug a hole out. Slipped underneath the fence.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.92,1:09:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,车在那边 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Get the truck over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.08,1:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,走着，老哥 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.88,1:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你想换我开会车吗 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You want me to drive for a while?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.44,1:10:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.84,1:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢坐在一个人旁边，不说话 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I know I feel comfortable with someone \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}when I can just sit, not talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.96,1:10:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯啊 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.32,1:11:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢只是坐着，不说话 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I just like sitting there, not talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.48,1:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我就感觉坐着很舒服，你知道 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I just feel comfortable sittin' there, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.12,1:11:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我这边伤口真得很疼哎 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I had a pain in my side real bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.16,1:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,疼得厉害啊 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}It's starting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.00,1:11:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能得怎么弄一下 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I think maybe I gotta do something with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.60,1:12:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不糟吧 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Don't look bad?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.24,1:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,把绷带盖回去 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}Let's put that bandage back on.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.84,1:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉不太妙啊，老哥 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I think it broke, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.64,1:13:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有汽油吗 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}You got any fuel?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.24,1:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,50美元 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}MAN: 50 US.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.80,1:13:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,50澳币 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}50 Australian.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.32,1:13:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只收美元 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}MAN: US dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.88,1:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有美元 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}I'm out of US.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.44,1:13:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我只收美元 \N{\fs14\c&HFAFAFD&\3c&HFC1202&}MAN: I only take American money.
